[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ねえ、クリセルダ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "なぁに、アンチュ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "このネックレスに使われてる石、私とクリセルダに\nよく似た色をしてる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふふ。よく分かったわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "せっかくのお揃いだもの。二人を連想できるような\n石を、一生懸命調合したのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "えへへ……これなら一緒にいても離れてても、\nクリセルダと一緒にいるみたい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そもそも一緒にいるときは一緒にいるでしょうに……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "アンチュ。あなた、先日の「自立する」という話は\nどうなったんです？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "えへへ……あれはあれ、これはこれなの。\n普段は自立できるように頑張ってるもん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "だから会えるときには、思う存分くっつくの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ。私もアンチュで癒されたいもの。\n思う存分くっつきましょ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ん……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "疲れた？　このまま眠っていいのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "んん……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ。すっかり幼くなってしまって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "安心してくれたのかしら",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（極夜の錬金党の歩みは幕を閉じたけれど――）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（こうして穏やかで、意外と楽しい今がある）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ふふ……\n　これも元錬金党のみんなのおかげかもしれないわね）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]